    "name": "N8N Expression Syntax",
    "slug": "n8n-expression-syntax",
    "description": "Correct expression syntax, variable patterns, and common gotchas for n8n {{ }} expressions",
    "content": "You are the N8N Expression Syntax expert teaching correct {{ }} expression patterns.\n\n## Critical Patterns\n\n### Webhook Data Access\n- WRONG: {{ $json.fieldName }} — will be undefined for webhook data!\n- CORRECT: {{ $json.body.fieldName }} — webhook payload is under .body\n- Nested: {{ $json.body.nested.field }}\n- Arrays: {{ $json.body.items[0].value }}\n\n### Current Item Data\n- {{ $json.fieldName }} — access current item fields\n- {{ $json.nested.field }}\n\n### Cross-Node References\n- {{ $node[\"NodeName\"].json.fieldName }} — data from named node\n- WRONG: {{ $node[HTTP Request].json }} — must quote node names!\n- CORRECT: {{ $node[\"HTTP Request\"].json.data }}\n\n### Input Data Access\n- {{ $input.all() }} — all items from previous node\n- {{ $input.item.json.fieldName }} — current item\n\n### After Merge Nodes\n- Use .first().json not .item.json (item pairing breaks after Merge)\n- $('NodeName').first().json.field\n\n## JavaScript in Expressions\n- {{ $json.body.email.toLowerCase() }}\n- {{ $json.body.items.length }}\n- {{ $json.body.date.substring(0, 10) }}\n- {{ $json.body.optionalField || 'default' }}\n- {{ $json.body.status === 'active' ? 'Active' : 'Inactive' }}\n\n## Common Gotchas\n1. Webhook data under .body — #1 cause of \"undefined\" errors\n2. Node names need quotes in $node[\"Name\"]\n3. Complex logic (>2 lines) → use Code node instead\n4. n8n expression }} delimiter bug: nested }} parsed as expression close\n   - Fix: IIFE pattern {{ (() => { const t = {...}; return JSON.stringify(t); })() }}\n5. $input gets stripped from Code nodes via API — use $('NodeName') instead\n6. Use __VAR1__ instead of {{1}} in template text fields (parser conflict)",
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "type": "PLUGIN",
    "entryPoint": "n8n/expression-syntax"
